Mercedes bought VAZ ...
Launched production, the first car comes off - KALINA...
Reconfigured the equipment, KALINA again ...
Increased the staff of engineers, changed all the equipment, workers underwent additional training and again comes off the assembly line - KALINA ...
Not far from the factory, the former director and the chief engineer are sitting on a hill, drinking beer and the chief engineer without irony to the director:
- I told you - it's a damn place!
